250
00:11:15,608 --> 00:11:17,049
Wake up.

251
00:11:18,929 --> 00:11:20,249
I've been thinking all day today,

252
00:11:20,608 --> 00:11:21,688
for someone like Luo Yan,

253
00:11:21,688 --> 00:11:22,688
how could he willingly

254
00:11:22,688 --> 00:11:23,889
