278
00:12:37,568 --> 00:12:38,289
Wait a moment.

279
00:12:38,769 --> 00:12:39,688
I'll be there soon.

280
00:12:59,769 --> 00:13:00,529
Young lady,

281
00:13:01,169 --> 00:13:02,169
you're punctual.

282
00:13:03,328 --> 00:13:04,688
